	- Shadowfax Simulator: [docs](./docs/tools/Simulator.md), [repository](https://github.com/ifit/shadowfax-simulator)
	
	### Summary
	
	Cloud runner for in-progress workouts. Manages workout data ingestion, transformation, and dispatch to the Shadowfax Event Broker (Kafka). This application is built to be pluggable, so implementing new behaviors should not require manipulating the `Core` kernel.
	
	### Plugins
	
	- Speed
	- Incline
	- Tick
	- Status
	
